{"id":178399,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-201199/","date":"2011-09-10T04:00:48Z","modified":"2011-09-10T05:36:25Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐  2011/9/9","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/sep/09/chinese-rights-activist-jailed-wang\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的维权活动家被判入狱九个月</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国法院以“寻衅滋事”为由将王荔蕻判决入狱，表明对异议分子的打压仍在继续</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110909/wl_nm/us_china_cisco\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">思科因涉嫌帮助中国镇压异议人士而被起诉</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国维权团体在美国对思科提起两场诉讼，有可能产生深远影响</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110909/wl_nm/us_china_xinjiang\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的反恐战争令新疆的民族关系裂痕</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">变</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">大</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110909/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_demolition\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国最高法院告诫地方政府避免强拆</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2011/sep/09/china-water-resettlement\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国南水北调的移民安置：老实人吃亏</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——尽管中国报纸在欢呼移民</span></span><span><span>34</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万人取得成功，但那些失去家园的人说的却是另外一套故事</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/09/09/school-food-poisoning/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的学校食物中毒现象</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国很多地方的学校午餐价格不是由学校制定，而是由政府制定。随着物价上涨，同样的钱吃到的东西质量在下降</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-09-09/china-food-price-gains-may-force-choice-between-inflation-jobs.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的食品价格增长或许将迫使政府在通胀和增长之间做出选择</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424053111903285704576556283401735332.html?mod=googlenews_wsj\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京玩起了指责外国人的游戏</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——前苏联的居民都知道，当政府报道外国出现某种灾害时，肯定是因为国内也出现了这样的灾害，现在中国官方媒体也在玩这样的游戏</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">电子胡同博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://siliconhutong.com/2011/09/07/its-media-chief-but-not-as-we-know-it/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">老大，这是我们所不熟悉的媒体</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的媒体管制机构在互联网上社交媒体面前有些不知所措。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110909/ap_on_re_as/as_china_corruption\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国将监控官员的出国旅行</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——当局希望以此避免贪官外逃或转移资产</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《大西洋》月刊：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2011/09/is-chinas-military-a-competitor-or-potential-ally/244792/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国军队是竞争对手还是潜在盟友</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？——对美国安全事务专家撰写的《</span></span><span><span>21</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">世纪亚洲盟友》报告的评论</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110909/pl_nm/us_china_usa_locke\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">骆家辉在北京外国语大学发表讲话，呼吁开放贸易，改善中美关系</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110909/pl_nm/us_china_usa_taiwan\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国官方报纸警告美国不要在台湾问题上玩火</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/simonmontlake/2011/09/08/big-sucking-sound-in-burma-is-chinas-resource-grab/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">缅甸的喧嚣是中国在攫取资源</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——外国人一直对缅甸的资源垂涎三尺。以前是英帝国的殖民者，现在则是中国公司。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/09/business/chinas-flawed-inflation-figures.html?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的通胀数字有所欠缺</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——食物价格所占比例过大和中国各地发展的不平衡，都使得中国的通胀数字并不能准确反映实际情况</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/09/09/us-china-economy-pboc-idUSTRE78822L20110909?feedType=RSS&#038;feedName=Yuan&#038;virtualBrandChannel=11721&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+reuters%2FUSyuanNews+%28News+%2F+US+%2F+YUAN+GCA%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国央行从各大国有银行收走</span>200<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">多亿元资金</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——据说这是对那些银行不遵守中央政策的惩罚，但这不会对国内资金流动造成多大影响</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8752665/China-to-build-worlds-biggest-airport.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国将建设世界最大的机场</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——北京计划建设大兴新机场，将设</span></span><span><span>9</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">条跑道，每天客流量达</span></span><span><span>34</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万人。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">程致宇：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://chovanec.wordpress.com/2011/09/09/apres-nous-le-deluge/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">出来混，迟早要还的</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——看看哈六药的大楼，就不难理解为什么中国的经济形势令人担心了。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">南开罗博：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://rob.easternity.com/?p=130\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在游泳池边看现代中国的典型人物（</span>1<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）：穿紧身泳裤的男人</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——这种人代表着那些看上去很傻，但是却很自豪的人</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；译者的音频博客已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；下载更新需翻墙。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-5858722011596666791?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[9154,8840]}